MUTANT42

In this mutant is introduced a interaction behavior fault: 

The mutated file is package net.sf.latexdraw.ui.LCanvas.
The mutated code is the operation paintViews.

To produce the failure:
1. Draw a shape on canvas by drag and drop.
 
Actual result:  The shape disappears after releasing the mouse button to complete the drawing. However, when the zoom is changed the shape appears.